 the borrowers whose lives would be destroyed if they purchased from 2004-2007.  <br/><br/>In the future when an industry insider has a conflicting view of products or practices that person should be sought out for a better understanding of their opinion.<br/><br/>This should be the case for wars or business.  Clearly, the foot soldiers have a much better idea of what is going on in the trenches than the Generals or Executives who sit behind a desk.</div>
