<a href="/akira/dtd/3981-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3981">Open Government Dialogue&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/8681-4049">jonathan.burgo</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">2 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Enact as law the following requirement for legislation: List all those who benefit and all who are hurt from a legislative initiative, and list why it is important to provide that benefit, and how the benefit outweighs the negitive impact. Further list the specific portion of the constitution that allows congress to pass (or even) consider the legislation.</div>
