<div id="Idea_3941"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3941-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3941">The Ninth Amendment is Real and Constitutional&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/8428-4049">sobi</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">2 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Inhibitions upon the people, as in prohibition, infringe upon the Ninth Amendment.<br/><br/>The White House needs to openly acknowledge this and encourage the Courts to protection the entire constitution, including, and currently, especially, the Ninth Amendment.<br/><br/>To the people.  Not the States.  Like the 2nd.  To the People.</div>
